PROVIDERS: Plugins for cloud APIs.
provider "aws" { region = "us-east-1" }
One config can manage AWS + GCP + Cloudflare simultaneously.

RESOURCES:
resource "aws_vpc" "main" { cidr_block = "10.0.0.0/16" }
resource "aws_subnet" "public" { vpc_id = aws_vpc.main.id }
References create implicit dependency graph.

MODULES: Reusable packages.
module "vpc" { source = "terraform-aws-modules/vpc/aws" }

STATE:
• Local: terraform.tfstate (learning)
• Remote: S3 + DynamoDB locking (teams, required)

VARIABLES + OUTPUTS: Parameterize and expose values.
